<p begin="24690000t" end="39590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle0">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="40700000t" end="73690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle1">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="74740000t" end="142770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle2">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="260920000t" end="304260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle3">&#x202a;果實宣告了未知的將來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="305300000t" end="374930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle4">&#x202a;夢想蛻變成理想&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="415410000t" end="496760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle5">&#x202a;任誰都渴望落幕…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="517180000t" end="532420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle6">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="533530000t" end="566180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle7">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="567230000t" end="618880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle8">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="619950000t" end="669550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle9">&#x202a;總有一天我會讓你看到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="670670000t" end="732670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle10">&#x202a;光輝閃耀的世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="810470000t" end="820140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle11">&#x202a;因為月…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="831160000t" end="856760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle12">&#x202a;是我第一個朋友&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="903900000t" end="920510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle13">&#x202a;海砂&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="921580000t" end="939210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle14">&#x202a;你可以拜託雷姆嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="940270000t" end="954600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle15">&#x202a;請雷姆殺死L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="968630000t" end="999910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle16">&#x202a;雷姆,我希望月能愛著我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1001000000t" end="1020680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle17">&#x202a;那就是我的幸福了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1049380000t" end="1058020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle18">&#x202a;好吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1065060000t" end="1081670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle19">&#x202a;我去殺了L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1091420000t" end="1103360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle20">&#x202a;L要死了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1115110000t" end="1126710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle21">&#x202a;這麼簡單…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1137460000t" end="1167150000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle22">&#x202a;第15話 賭注&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1176840000t" end="1192420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle23">&#x202a;那麼,要何時動手?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1200530000t" end="1244220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle24">&#x202a;只要帶我去他那邊&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我就能馬上殺了他&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1245240000t" end="1270490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle25">&#x202a;越快越好,明天也行&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1278940000t" end="1309200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle26">&#x202a;不過現在就下決定太趕了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1321320000t" end="1362280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle27">&#x202a;今晚我會仔細想想明天再告訴你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1363360000t" end="1372340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle28">&#x202a;我知道了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1378370000t" end="1399300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle29">&#x202a;聽好了,無論發生任何情況&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1400390000t" end="1424050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle30">&#x202a;在得到我的指示前不要殺了他&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1425090000t" end="1443060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle31">&#x202a;任何情況都不行&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1444100000t" end="1476410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle32">&#x202a;好,這個我可以答應你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1477470000t" end="1492710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle33">&#x202a;但只限於L這件事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1502500000t" end="1530140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle34">&#x202a;海砂,告訴我你的手機號碼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1531190000t" end="1548820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle35">&#x202a;現在才問太晚了吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1549880000t" end="1569220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle36">&#x202a;月的也要告訴我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1570230000t" end="1593550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle37">&#x202a;我的手機號碼不能告訴你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1594590000t" end="1626900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle38">&#x202a;為什麼,我們是情侶耶&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;不能這樣啦&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1632630000t" end="1663230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle39">&#x202a;不是跟你說了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我已經被警察盯上了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1664320000t" end="1705960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle40">&#x202a;現在的警方&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;有權監聽某些特定電話的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1734060000t" end="1752370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle41">&#x202a;那麼,就用這個吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1753410000t" end="1772750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle42">&#x202a;給你一個我的手機&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1773770000t" end="1800050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle43">&#x202a;為了不同的用途&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我特地準備了3個&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1807130000t" end="1820780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle44">&#x202a;真是個好主意&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1821820000t" end="1839110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle45">&#x202a;用你的就沒問題了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1840170000t" end="1851430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle46">&#x202a;太好了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1852510000t" end="1886180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle47">&#x202a;我會每天跟你&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;愛的熱線和傳一堆簡訊的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1887210000t" end="1906210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle48">&#x202a;我會把電源關掉&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1907230000t" end="1947160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle49">&#x202a;即使要通電話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也得等我主動打電話給你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1958620000t" end="1974540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle50">&#x202a;怎麼這樣&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1975640000t" end="1996910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle51">&#x202a;那你什麼時候會打給我?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1997990000t" end="2014940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle52">&#x202a;大概是明天&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2016010000t" end="2057650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle53">&#x202a;無論明天要不要動手殺了L&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我都會聯絡你的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2064060000t" end="2076680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle54">&#x202a;明天嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2077740000t" end="2119380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle55">&#x202a;雖然不是什麼甜言蜜語&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;但是結束後再來也行&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2120450000t" end="2145360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle56">&#x202a;那麼海砂,今天你就先回去吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2151140000t" end="2171390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle57">&#x202a;為什麼,不是才7點嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2172500000t" end="2194110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle58">&#x202a;現在起才是情侶的時間呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2195190000t" end="2220440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle59">&#x202a;我們兩個人一起去吃飯&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;一起看夜景&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2221550000t" end="2244530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle60">&#x202a;然後就是最浪漫的時間了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2250910000t" end="2258530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle61">&#x202a;海砂&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2371700000t" end="2399680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle62">&#x202a;聽話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;今天就先回去吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2410400000t" end="2418020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle63">&#x202a;好的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2423750000t" end="2451730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle64">&#x202a;那麼你在外面和雷姆交談的時候&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2452780000t" end="2489410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle65">&#x202a;一定要注意有沒有人偷聽&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;盡量小聲點&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2490480000t" end="2510160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle66">&#x202a;我跟路克也都是這樣的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2511170000t" end="2522090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle67">&#x202a;好的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2523180000t" end="2544110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle68">&#x202a;打擾了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2545200000t" end="2574550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle69">&#x202a;海砂小姐,明天也要來喔&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2608930000t" end="2638280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle70">&#x202a;不過你突然吻她真是嚇壞我了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2639300000t" end="2675590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle71">&#x202a;我有必要和海砂變得親近一點&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2690020000t" end="2724940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle72">&#x202a;先不說這個&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;明天究竟該不該殺L呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2726050000t" end="2759720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle73">&#x202a;在他還沒以L的身份&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;公開露面就死的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2760750000t" end="2807740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle74">&#x202a;我必須做好&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;嫌疑加深的心理準備&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2808800000t" end="2822790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle75">&#x202a;原來如此&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2823820000t" end="2874790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle76">&#x202a;我以為你被他當成朋友&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;所以在猶豫該不該殺他呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2875870000t" end="2909200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle77">&#x202a;朋友?我只是附和他的話而已&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2910240000t" end="2918880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle78">&#x202a;一開始我就說了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2919910000t" end="2956200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle79">&#x202a;如果他想跟我做朋友&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我就奉陪到底&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2961620000t" end="2993930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle80">&#x202a;流河是夜神月表面上的朋友&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2994990000t" end="3010570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle81">&#x202a;L是KIRA的敵人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3101430000t" end="3124750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle82">&#x202a;沒錯,L是敵人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3132790000t" end="3163390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle83">&#x202a;既然流河向我表明身份&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就應該殺了他&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3172500000t" end="3193770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle84">&#x202a;只要將L設計為意外死亡的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3194850000t" end="3228520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle85">&#x202a;幾乎不會有人懷疑我是KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3229550000t" end="3247520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle86">&#x202a;就算有也沒證據&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3257250000t" end="3287170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle87">&#x202a;只能先想想L死後&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我該怎麼行動了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3293620000t" end="3307950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle88">&#x202a;這是一場賭注&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3323980000t" end="3340930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle89">&#x202a;明天就是L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3342000000t" end="3388640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle90">&#x202a;不,至少是龍崎流河的忌日了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3455450000t" end="3464090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle91">&#x202a;毛髮&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3492150000t" end="3507390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle92">&#x202a;小吃店吃剩的點心屑&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3539200000t" end="3546820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle93">&#x202a;毛髮&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3571560000t" end="3580540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle94">&#x202a;夜神先生&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3594920000t" end="3625860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle95">&#x202a;如果近期內我死了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;那令郎就是KIRA了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3648640000t" end="3658310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle96">&#x202a;又是毛髮&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3681340000t" end="3698290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle97">&#x202a;龍崎,剛才你說什麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3699360000t" end="3724610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle98">&#x202a;是呀,你在說什麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3725720000t" end="3773730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle99">&#x202a;到時候渡就任你們差遣&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;接下來的就拜託你們了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3774770000t" end="3788420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle100">&#x202a;龍崎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3789450000t" end="3813110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle101">&#x202a;雖然你嘴巴上說&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;他幾乎沒有嫌疑了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3814140000t" end="3839740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle102">&#x202a;但是內心裡&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;究竟有多懷疑我兒子?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3846170000t" end="3873810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle103">&#x202a;我也不知道&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我心裡究竟是怎麼想的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3889880000t" end="3909220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle104">&#x202a;以前沒碰過這種情況&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3918580000t" end="3943260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle105">&#x202a;如果KIRA和第二KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;已經聯繫上的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3944270000t" end="3965540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle106">&#x202a;那我就很危險了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3966620000t" end="4022250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle107">&#x202a;所以我或許已經無法冷靜&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;分析自己的想法了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4056050000t" end="4094390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle108">&#x202a;或許是沒別的可疑對象&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;所以只能鎖定他而已&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4101760000t" end="4133390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle109">&#x202a;即使如此&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;如果我現在被殺的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4134460000t" end="4156760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle110">&#x202a;請你斷定令郎就是KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4195850000t" end="4229520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle111">&#x202a;這種突如其來的指示&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也是情非得已的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4230550000t" end="4250230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle112">&#x202a;這時候只能賭一賭了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4383710000t" end="4398950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle113">&#x202a;沒那回事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4400060000t" end="4418370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle114">&#x202a;我只不過抓住了要領而已&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4480140000t" end="4489120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle115">&#x202a;怎麼了?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4541200000t" end="4554510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle116">&#x202a;夜神同學&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4566220000t" end="4574860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle117">&#x202a;你好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4599920000t" end="4643610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle118">&#x202a;高田同學,我想跟他單獨聊一下&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;待會見了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4652980000t" end="4661280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle119">&#x202a;好的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4700360000t" end="4723680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle120">&#x202a;你的女朋友不會介意吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4724720000t" end="4762030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle121">&#x202a;別說這個了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你不是害怕在人前露面的嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4763090000t" end="4775030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle122">&#x202a;沒關係嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4776100000t" end="4810680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle123">&#x202a;我發現到&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;只要你不是KIRA就沒關係了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4817810000t" end="4850800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle124">&#x202a;在外面知道我是L的&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就只有你了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4858180000t" end="4888100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle125">&#x202a;我已經這麼對搜查總部的人說了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4894550000t" end="4933230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle126">&#x202a;要是近期內我被殺了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就可以斷定夜神月就是KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4951610000t" end="4960930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle127">&#x202a;這傢伙…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4991650000t" end="5032610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle128">&#x202a;你也說我休學後你覺得很寂寞&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5033690000t" end="5055640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle129">&#x202a;所以我決定來換換心情&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5063720000t" end="5090000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle130">&#x202a;不會死的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;大學是個愉快的地方&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5091080000t" end="5108710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle131">&#x202a;是啊,你一不在&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5109770000t" end="5140710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle132">&#x202a;夠水準跟我聊天的人都沒了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;無聊死了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5141800000t" end="5164780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle133">&#x202a;所以才找上高田同學嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5165820000t" end="5179810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle134">&#x202a;差不多吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5200520000t" end="5238180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle135">&#x202a;今天殺了這傢伙沒問題嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5239230000t" end="5280870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle136">&#x202a;不,這傢伙在我&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;還在猶豫的時候突然現身&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5281940000t" end="5305600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle137">&#x202a;來動搖我的決心&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5306630000t" end="5331310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle138">&#x202a;恐怕是為了來試探我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5340660000t" end="5366940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle139">&#x202a;這樣不就正中他下懷了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5379700000t" end="5404380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle140">&#x202a;一起去學生餐廳吃蛋糕吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5405400000t" end="5433730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle141">&#x202a;好,反正我下一堂沒課&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5434760000t" end="5447380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle142">&#x202a;那真是太好了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5462120000t" end="5482710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle143">&#x202a;不知道有沒有奶油蛋糕&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5483810000t" end="5505420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle144">&#x202a;我也不知道&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5509830000t" end="5530420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle145">&#x202a;月,找到你了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5542200000t" end="5569840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle146">&#x202a;我剛好在附近拍照,就順便來了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5570890000t" end="5592160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle147">&#x202a;海砂&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這個笨蛋&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5593250000t" end="5608830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle148">&#x202a;你是月的朋友?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5609930000t" end="5627220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle149">&#x202a;你的造型真有特色&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5641300000t" end="5663250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle150">&#x202a;不,我贏了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5664320000t" end="5690600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle151">&#x202a;海砂可以看到流河的本名&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5696690000t" end="5731050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle152">&#x202a;我是月的女朋友,彌海砂&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;請多指教&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5738390000t" end="5750670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle153">&#x202a;我是流河旱樹&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5761750000t" end="5774370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle154">&#x202a;流河旱樹…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5783770000t" end="5819040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle155">&#x202a;這傢伙跟那個偶像同名同姓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5820140000t" end="5830380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle156">&#x202a;很有趣吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5837830000t" end="5865810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle157">&#x202a;但是跟我看到的名字不一樣…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5873200000t" end="5915520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle158">&#x202a;流河,你的出現造成反效果了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5961280000t" end="5980620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle159">&#x202a;為什麼笑得這麼詭異&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5981640000t" end="6009280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle160">&#x202a;難道他發現了?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6010330000t" end="6058340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle161">&#x202a;如果發現她可能是第二KIRA的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;應該笑不出來吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6072390000t" end="6082280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle162">&#x202a;夜神&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6107100000t" end="6120410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle163">&#x202a;我好羨慕你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6136130000t" end="6168780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle164">&#x202a;我從「EIGHTEEN」 8月號起&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就是海砂的迷了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6169830000t" end="6194170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle165">&#x202a;真的嗎?我好高興&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6195180000t" end="6213490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle166">&#x202a;那個女孩不就是MISAMISA嗎&#x202c;</p>
