<p begin="10405060000t" end="10430660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle268">&#x202a;你的話應該可以立刻殺了我吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10456440000t" end="10477370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle269">&#x202a;海砂,難道說…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10478460000t" end="10497460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle270">&#x202a;沒錯,殺了我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10503820000t" end="10526460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle271">&#x202a;你是要我殺了你?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10527510000t" end="10547420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle272">&#x202a;沒錯,殺了我吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10567890000t" end="10597810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle273">&#x202a;我無法忍受了,殺了我吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10607930000t" end="10639560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle274">&#x202a;殺了海砂的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我也要殺了夜神月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10640630000t" end="10656900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle275">&#x202a;這樣也可以嗎&#x202c;</p>
