<p begin="10697680000t" end="10734310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle277">&#x202a;你竟然這麼願意為那傢伙而死&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10753740000t" end="10779340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle278">&#x202a;算了,如果不殺我的話…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10780430000t" end="10801360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle279">&#x202a;不妙,不要讓她咬舌自盡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10876860000t" end="10921230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle280">&#x202a;難道是KIRA控制了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;她的死前行為?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10940590000t" end="10964930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle281">&#x202a;雷姆,怎麼突然跑來了&#x202c;</p>
