<p begin="11123440000t" end="11154720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle286">&#x202a;當她身心都達到極限時&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11155810000t" end="11183110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle287">&#x202a;她開始要求我殺了她&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11200520000t" end="11227480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle288">&#x202a;這全是為了得到你的愛&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11255240000t" end="11291190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle289">&#x202a;無論海砂怎麼求我&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我都下不了手&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11292280000t" end="11307520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle290">&#x202a;我看不下去了&#x202c;</p>
