<p begin="11665980000t" end="11711600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle302">&#x202a;你會忘了所有關於死神的事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11735720000t" end="11789760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle303">&#x202a;放心吧,海砂喜歡的人是夜神月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11790770000t" end="11814770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle304">&#x202a;這份感情會被保留下來的&#x202c;</p>
