<p begin="12409390000t" end="12423380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle313">&#x202a;我知道對你來說&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12424410000t" end="12459330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle314">&#x202a;這是最好的辦法&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12460440000t" end="12484780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle315">&#x202a;所以我才會向海砂提議的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12497810000t" end="12535120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle316">&#x202a;你不救她出來的話,我就殺了你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12621600000t" end="12640940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle317">&#x202a;我知道了,雷姆&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12641960000t" end="12668580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle318">&#x202a;我大概知道L下一步會怎麼走了&#x202c;</p>
