<p begin="12857170000t" end="12910870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle322">&#x202a;捨棄所有不需要的事物&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12911890000t" end="12943860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle323">&#x202a;無法割捨的感情&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12944930000t" end="12999310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle324">&#x202a;深藏在我的心裡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13000320000t" end="13064030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle325">&#x202a;依然處在現實與理想的夾縫中&#x202c;</p>
