<p begin="13168480000t" end="13236510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle328">&#x202a;因為我有一顆強烈追求的心&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13246230000t" end="13293900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle329">&#x202a;虛偽恐懼虛飾憂愁&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13294940000t" end="13349320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle330">&#x202a;面對各種負面情緒&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13350330000t" end="13404370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle331">&#x202a;我也不會弱到被擊垮&#x202c;</p>
